{
  "stem": "1917.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In our group, there were about seven or eight sets of twins.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were under SS supervision.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "An SS was-- one or two SS were accompanying us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was one grown up, one mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I could never really figure out how she got to even stay with her children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Her name was Mrs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Changeri.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She lives in Israel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She's still alive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we were going through this very tall barbed wire, and finally, from one camp into another, and were taken into a building that-- was a brick building.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Was huge.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We were ordered to undress.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Our clothes were taken away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we were sitting on bleachers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Quite frankly, I don't think that any human being can ever be prepared for a place like Auschwitz, no matter how much persecution before then.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I thought for a while  it seemed like I am watching something that-- it's not really relating to me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I was numb.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I closed my eyes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I said, maybe this is a nightmare.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And if I close them and open them up again, maybe the whole thing will disappear.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We sat there naked in the company of complete strangers for the better part of the day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Later on in the afternoon, we were lined up for registration and tattooing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They cut our braids down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And Mrs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Changeri's head was shaved.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And the so-called barber explained that we are privileged because we are twins.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we are permitted to have our own hair.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Then we were lined up for registration and tattooing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And when my turn came, I decided that I was going to fight back, that I was not going to let them do to me whatever they wanted without fighting back.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
